# e2e_objectstores (Data Source)
DataSource will list all the created Resources of nodes.

# Example uses
```hcl 
data "e2e_objectstores" "eos12345"{
  region=<bucket_region: string> (default: "Delhi")
  project_id=<project_id: int>
}
```
